WEBVTT

00:00:59.902 --> 00:01:03.579
with no contact with my family.

00:01:03.579 --> 00:01:07.000
In this place I sat

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:09.226
in a class like that

00:01:09.226 --> 00:01:12.978
with more than 150 other kids,

00:01:12.978 --> 00:01:15.470
and for six years.

00:01:15.470 --> 00:01:19.550
In this time, it just happened to me to come to school

00:01:19.550 --> 00:01:25.245
to realize that my classmate died.

00:01:25.245 --> 00:01:29.758
Today, not so much has changed.

00:01:29.758 --> 00:01:34.211
There is still no electricity in my village.